12:54.065 --> 12:55.271
Jerry,
stop, please, okay?

12:55.358 --> 12:56.848
We weren't even
supposed to be down here.

12:56.943 --> 12:58.149
If we confront him
about this --

12:58.236 --> 12:59.772
Oh, my god!
I love this.

12:59.862 --> 13:02.274
