how far you will go for him.

13:02.365 --> 13:04.652
You want to go upstairs
and cut carrots

13:04.742 --> 13:06.278
and watch
a Lifetime original

13:06.369 --> 13:08.861
above a fucking
alien dungeon!

13:08.955 --> 13:11.788
Your relationship with
your father is psychotic.

13:11.874 --> 13:13.285
