is a bad person.

13:15.253 --> 13:16.869
Step out of your ego
for a second

13:16.963 --> 13:18.829
and look at this thing --
it's a monster.

13:18.923 --> 13:20.163
He might
have it chained up

13:20.258 --> 13:21.748
so that it doesn't
eat the planet!

13:21.843 --> 13:24.005
Right, because your father's
such an altruist?

13:24.095 --> 13:27.679
I once saw him briefly
forget the word for "Humans."

13:27.765 --> 13:29.881
