13:46.409 --> 13:48.241
at the Galactic Federation
in an hour.

13:48.328 --> 13:49.318
Oh, I'll never make it.

13:49.412 --> 13:50.948
Ah, I'll push it
to next week.

13:51.039 --> 13:52.996
Unity, could you get Rick
out here, please?

13:53.082 --> 13:54.618
He's unavailable.
He's...

13:54.709 --> 13:56.325
...having sex with you.
We get it. Gross.

13:56.419 --> 13:57.659
Get him out here now.

13:57.754 --> 13:58.789
I don't think
he wants to be --

13:58.880 --> 14:01.042
- Grandpa Rick!
- Rick! Rick!

14:01.132 --> 14:02.839
I'm gonna tell Mom and Dad
about the gagoo

14:02.925 --> 14:04.256
you have locked up
under the garage!

14:04.344 --> 14:06.881
What the hell is your problem?

14:06.971 --> 14:08.928
