we need to go home, now.

14:09.015 --> 14:10.801
Fine. Sheesh.

14:13.436 --> 14:14.892
See you.

14:14.979 --> 14:16.686
Uh, Rick,
I think we should all go.

14:16.773 --> 14:18.980
