Unity.

15:38.229 --> 15:40.436
I'm not looking for judgment,
just a yes or no --

15:40.523 --> 15:42.389
can you assimilate
a giraffe?

15:42.483 --> 15:43.268
You're the worst!

15:43.359 --> 15:46.101
