You don't support this family!

15:46.195 --> 15:47.560
All you care about
is yourself!

15:47.655 --> 15:48.861
You think supporting the family
is about supporting you emotionally...

15:48.948 --> 15:50.484
you've got two children
being dragged across the cosmos

15:50.575 --> 15:51.906
...because it's never
enough, Jerry!

15:51.993 --> 15:53.108
...by your dangerously
ill father!

15:53.202 --> 15:54.408
And you force me to
watch it happen...

15:54.495 --> 15:56.987
...because you'd rather
lose them and lose me...

15:57.081 --> 15:58.446
