to cure my disease

16:38.414 --> 16:40.496
was not to save my life
or anyone else's,

16:40.583 --> 16:43.746
but to patent and sell the cure
for billions of blemflarcks.

16:43.836 --> 16:45.292
But you know
the reason why

16:45.379 --> 16:47.336
I ripped my chains
out of the wall?

16:47.423 --> 16:50.211
And do you know why I'm never
coming back to this planet?

16:50.301 --> 16:54.169
Because the two of you
are the fucking worst!

16:54.263 --> 16:56.846
You both hate yourselves
and each other.

16:56.933 --> 16:59.174
And the idea that it has
anything to do with Rick

16:59.268 --> 17:00.804
is laughable.

17:00.895 --> 17:03.057
I'd laugh,
but I'm biologically incapable.

17:03.147 --> 17:04.854
<i>That's</i> how alien I am.

17:04.941 --> 17:07.308
And even I'm sitting here
listening to the two of you

17:07.401 --> 17:10.233
and being like,
"What the fuck"!

17:10.320 --> 17:12.436
So good luck
with your shitty marriage,

17:12.531 --> 17:15.569
and tell Rick I'm sorry he has
to deal with <i>either</i> of you.

17:15.660 --> 17:18.027
Blim Blam out.

17:22.959 --> 17:25.371
You know what?
I'm taking this.

17:28.756 --> 17:31.544
How do you --
what is this?

17:34.178 --> 17:37.011
